        <mxCell id="caption" value="&lt;i&gt;Control segment (PKGINFO, install scripts, checksums) is byte-for-byte preserved — so apk-tools on the device sees Alpine's package metadata, scripts, and file deps unchanged.&lt;/i&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=11;fontColor=#666666;" parent="1" vertex="1">
